snippet.textDisplay:
First of all, Coke Studio has already made a lot of noise from above.
Don't wait so long, otherwise we will be angry.
This song is about mehndi, marriage,
Well set, music, singers, rap,
A new style of drum is appearing,
  Poetry, dance, colorful dressing, phool hi phool, the director worked so hard on every frame.
Where did this idea come from?
  Believe me, this song is a lot of fun to listen to as well as watch.
  Singing the right song from Sabri Sister is a feat of music director alone.
I am saying with full confidence that I will play this song for every wedding, mehndi in Pakistan.
Write it down and there will be a dance on it.
